    "name": "Lorne",
    "steam_appid": 2172970,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lorne is a third person adventure game set in a beautiful open world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are a ranger of Lorne, who has to build a bastion to withstand the coming invasion. Survive wave after wave of attackers and keep improving your defenses. Can you defeat all 3 Vassals of Evil?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the world of Lorne for hidden artifacts that unlocks new powers and technologies. Improve your bastion and keep your Powercore safe, no matter the cost.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Pressure.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TEST YOUR GRIT AND WIT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go up against shrines filled with challenges and bosses to see what you're made of, and score some extra loot to help you in your endeavors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/2dfb68ce8512cf8e4deb15fa6b749f0d.poster.avif?t=1772105883\" width=1170 height=627 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/2dfb68ce8512cf8e4deb15fa6b749f0d.webm?t=1772105883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CRAFT POWERFUL ARTIFACTS</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Lorne, you must do whatever it takes to become strong enough to defend your home. Craft items using resources harvested from the world, upgrade your abilities with soul fragments, and explore the land to uncover ancient trinkets that grant untold power. Or, seek out powerful bosses in their lairs, defeat them, and claim legendary loot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/76769f48a7ac85ca1816ea0036bca568.poster.avif?t=1772105883\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/76769f48a7ac85ca1816ea0036bca568.webm?t=1772105883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/76769f48a7ac85ca1816ea0036bca568.mp4?t=1772105883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUILD A BASTION OF JUSTICE</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Claim land and create a base, tailored for the perfect defense. Upgrade, and design your own own fortifications. withstand wave after wave crashing over your ramparts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/e9f85fbb0487b5e37e89496da1b12c73.poster.avif?t=1772105883\" width=800 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/e9f85fbb0487b5e37e89496da1b12c73.webm?t=1772105883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/e9f85fbb0487b5e37e89496da1b12c73.mp4?t=1772105883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE INVASION</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you start the game, the clock is ticking. The invasion is coming, and each wave is a little stronger than the last. Plantlings, Evil Mages, Stumplings, Elementals, hordes of Undead, and World Bosses the enemy forces are after one thing the total destruction of your Powercore, and with it, Lorne.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/0bc740ae54d934c2e3bc9564b80aacf7.poster.avif?t=1772105883\" width=1100 height=588 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/0bc740ae54d934c2e3bc9564b80aacf7.webm?t=1772105883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/0bc740ae54d934c2e3bc9564b80aacf7.mp4?t=1772105883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DO YOUR DUTY AS A RANGER</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do what you need to do in order to protect Lorne. As a ranger you investigate conflicts, uncover mysteries or find ways to take down dangerous mythical creatures. You guard the borders and roam the lands, all to keep the peace of Lorne.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/c22c8f1f53ad276484eb7cd1a05d3cf3.poster.avif?t=1772105883\" width=800 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/c22c8f1f53ad276484eb7cd1a05d3cf3.webm?t=1772105883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/c22c8f1f53ad276484eb7cd1a05d3cf3.mp4?t=1772105883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/dbbd3d7226ed77fa1bc0300a589f8c93.poster.avif?t=1772105883\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/dbbd3d7226ed77fa1bc0300a589f8c93.webm?t=1772105883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172970/extras/dbbd3d7226ed77fa1bc0300a589f8c93.mp4?t=1772105883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
